<title>USA: Arrow Electronics renews share repurchase.</title>
<headline>Arrow Electronics renews share repurchase.</headline>
<dateline>MELVILLE, N.Y. 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Arrow Electronics Inc said on Tuesday that its board as renewed the stock repurchase program that it had started last year with an authorization to buy up to $50 million of its common stock.</p>
<p>The purchases will be made in the open market or in privately negotiated transactions, Arrow said.</p>
<p>The company has approximately 50 million shares outstanding.</p>
